{"tid":2148122,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"利用「多啦A夢」改圖誘青少年食大麻警放蛇拘41男女撿132萬元毒品","createTime":"2020-08-09T17:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T18:52:59.000Z","uid":134739,"like":9,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad1ec66a95bd42e5804aa309ff35cb9c9daf52b","tid":2148122,"uid":134739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0U8Sid9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0U8Sid9.jpg&h=af4b3895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方發現在網上社交平台販賣大麻有上升趨勢，毒販利用Instagram、Facebook及Telegram等熱門流行平台，明碼實價兜售大麻，情況達到肆無忌憚、明目張膽的地步，毒品調查科由6月開始展開行動，派員放蛇在網上平台喬裝買家，鎖定目標，在過去一連三日拘捕41名男女，年齡14至45歲，其中5名為未成年人士，共撿獲約132萬元毒品。有毒犯利用受歡迎的漫畫人物改圖，降低青少年對吸食毒品的戒心，調查又顯示網上流傳很多大麻的相關搜尋關鍵字，警方已要求社交媒體公司刪除相關的違法帖文。<br />\n<br />\n警方經調查後發現有30個有關該類的社交媒體帳戶，於是喬裝買家，連同港島總區刑事部人員，在本月4至6日共拘捕41人，34男7女，年齡14至45歲，<strong><span class=\"red\">5人為未成年人士，被捕者有5人是中學生、2人是大專生</span></strong>，18人無業，其餘從事不同職業，部份人有黑社會背景。41人共涉及48宗販運危險藥物案件，撿獲共5.1公斤大麻草、9支大麻油、264克Ｋ仔、44克冰毒等，市值132萬元。其中一名男子被控販毒今日提堂，其餘大部份被捕人士獲保釋候查。<strong><span class=\"red\">警方指當中有兩名被捕人士，於去年反修例事件因刑事毀壞被捕。</span><br />\n</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200807/3THZQ3NNKFUMH75PQXIJFOSVPE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200807%2F3THZQ3NNKFUMH75PQXIJFOSVPE%2F&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25Yp1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=34c67f61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200807%2F3THZQ3NNKFUMH75PQXIJFOSVPE%2F&h=21161e52\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200807/3THZQ3NNKFUMH75PQXIJFOSVPE/</a>"},{"pid":"d6e0e1efcfb1edde4924fb337d21338300583f65","tid":2148122,"uid":134739,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:18:47.000Z","msg":"利用多啦A 夢誘青少年肛交就話驚姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909d55426a72571726d749ba62933e1927590fcc","tid":2148122,"uid":204929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:20:27.000Z","msg":"真身係咪黑警引誘𡃁仔入職<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"0d4da055d1f1f6dc917a39e86a92b5699db25da2","tid":2148122,"uid":103521,"like":21,"dislike":5,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:21:46.000Z","msg":"大麻係撚毒品"},{"pid":"0f8ef46d520a205a42fba6d9143f7dcf8d1f2f42","tid":2148122,"uid":59976,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:26:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgflip.com/2zz3dg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgflip.com%2F2zz3dg.jpg&h=4ed332a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47d69bda42f69e301030446697f364fe6a8a8ab0","tid":2148122,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:26:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQRtfSs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQRtfSs.png&h=c5d0d0d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd961031ccb4d41c24e5d4dd138fb7f48e4a5a19","tid":2148122,"uid":15866,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:28:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span class=\"red\"><strong>警方指當中有兩名被捕人士，於去年反修例事件因刑事毀壞被捕。</strong></span></blockquote><br />\n手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2176ea2081485c4b82c32cead4d429f2c824e796","tid":2148122,"uid":282352,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0d4da055d1f1f6dc917a39e86a92b5699db25da2","tid":2148122,"uid":103521,"like":21,"dislike":5,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:21:46.000Z","msg":"大麻係撚毒品"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T17:29:31.000Z","msg":"大麻師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3def7f4612cefca2cdbb42037b88f6151ba3db29","tid":2148122,"uid":3167,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"